// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1596 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: bb42d79c-059f-52e9-81c7-7670dd85479d

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *amazonlinux:1* OR ImageFileName = *debian:7* OR ImageFileName = *debian:8*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
